"{\"content\":{\"body\":\"## My search for an acre of escape\\n\\n[![Paul Greenberg](https://miro.medium.com/fit/c/56/56/1\\\\*tPfbBeQ23qMKUptWlw1FaQ.jpeg)](https://4fishgreenberg.medium.com/?source=post_page-----82252fbaae82-----------------------------------)\\n\\n![](https://miro.medium.com/max/1400/1\\\\*lvzvn8HdxUe8BXEsPxlZ5w.png)\\n\\n“Granite erratic, Dudmaston” by Richard Webb is licensed under CC BY-SA 2.0. To view a copy of this license, visit <https://creativecommons.org/licenses/by-sa/2.0/?ref=openverse&atype=rich>\\n\\nIt was the rock that caught my eye. Dappled with lichen and lighted by the afternoon sun, it appeared to be the perfect place for contemplation. A spot where you could sit and write your novel, ponder your place in the universe, and perhaps reach some kind of equilibrium with the planet.\\n\",\"timestamp\":1641077263,\"title\":\"Is Anywhere Safe from Climate Change? - Paul Greenberg - Medium\"},\"digest\":\"FfR6dU0ibBmGmt8hIwwbH-Nb_9uAk6vkrATwy8XNkh8\",\"authorship\":{\"contributor\":\"0x31356557D88e89638E00c91B5FE65Ba144Cd567F\",\"signingKey\":\"{\\\"crv\\\":\\\"P-256\\\",\\\"ext\\\":true,\\\"key_ops\\\":[\\\"verify\\\"],\\\"kty\\\":\\\"EC\\\",\\\"x\\\":\\\"YeHE5qRnMI9ykYsTV_96ZVv6cwRvyVfnZmDyZmZ4KU0\\\",\\\"y\\\":\\\"F9Dd-hmjJ1qEnwHtv_l9ukTNReoTcQsPl6SRJTMRVfo\\\"}\",\"signature\":\"fe2WNK1fbPSXgVhh6goCU0F1ufILOMCQUK0lyjThTH9vKi46CHwUXUdfifjB-PmTAI5lX-wC3pCNf-Aju5k_5g\",\"signingKeySignature\":\"0xf6d990c28a7686793f67b5520c9712acb46ca34688cfb8a74de058274f3300ea2f9b3c3a6bd054eeae9bd476babbea57e2219a47ef74385ef7d664ba8e2114191c\",\"signingKeyMessage\":\"I authorize publishing on mirror.xyz from this device using:\\n{\\\"crv\\\":\\\"P-256\\\",\\\"ext\\\":true,\\\"key_ops\\\":[\\\"verify\\\"],\\\"kty\\\":\\\"EC\\\",\\\"x\\\":\\\"YeHE5qRnMI9ykYsTV_96ZVv6cwRvyVfnZmDyZmZ4KU0\\\",\\\"y\\\":\\\"F9Dd-hmjJ1qEnwHtv_l9ukTNReoTcQsPl6SRJTMRVfo\\\"}\",\"algorithm\":{\"name\":\"ECDSA\",\"hash\":\"SHA-256\"}},\"nft\":{},\"version\":\"12-21-2020\",\"origi